//
// Regression for #2463: cyclostatic acquire inside scf.for. The IRON design
// in test.py declares the cyclostatic core; the peel rewrite turns the
// in-body AcquireGreaterEqual(3) into a steady-state delta of 1 so the
// producer-side lock drains instead of deadlocking.
//
// REQUIRES: ryzen_ai_npu2, peano, xrt_python_bindings
//
// RUN: %run_on_npu2% %python %S/test.py
